description.et:
Presentation about a variety of English (20 pts max.), which complies with the following criteria:
1. made using PowerPoint or a similar software;
2. complies with time limit (10-15 minutes);
3. has an adequate number of slides (10-15 slides);
4. includes the main aspects:
* short historical overview of the origin of the variety
* where and by whom it is spoken / spheres and status of use
* pronunciation (phonology)
* grammar (morphology and syntax )
* vocabulary (lexis)
* example (audio or video)
5. slides are not overloaded with information & contain only main points;
6. slides provide practical examples of theoretical points;
7. font size is big enough;
8. background, design and visuals are not disturbing;
9. language is correct, clear and easy to understand;
10. presenters speak themselves and look at their notes only occasionally;
11. presenters maintain visual and verbal contact with the audience, they are standing when talking;
12. presenters' pronunciation is correct, clear and comprehensible;
13. presenters know their topic and the meanings of the words they are using
